--1. Created the Dev profile: `hermes profile create --name dev`
--2. Migrated core memory from `software-engineer/memories/core/` to `dev/memories/core/`
--3. Added explicit scope constraint: *"You are a Dev persona. Your expertise is writing, testing, and deploying code. You do NOT provide architectural advice beyond implementation — that belongs to the Orchestrator."*
--4. Updated all routing rules from `software-engineer` to `dev` in the Orchestrator's memory
--5. Archived old profile: `mv ~/.hermes/profiles/software-engineer ~/.hermes/profiles/archived/software-engineer-20260622`
